724770f-a.text:
Whitehall Street, east side, at Bridge Street, showing the lower stories of the Kemble Building, No. 15-25. In the foreground are W.P.A.
employees engaged in a track removal project.
September 14, 1936.
W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Art Project.
